OL,3,CTop of the Klopps: Jurgen's best quotes
OL,5,FSince day one, Jurgen Klopp has kept
OL,6,Fhis heart on his sleeve, and his words
OL,7,Foff the cuff.
OL,9,FWhile media duties haven't been his
OL,10,Ffavourite part of the job, he
OL,11,Fcertainly gave great copy.
OL,13,FCanning the cliches and shunning the
OL,14,Fstatus quo - he's gifted us with some
OL,15,Fincredible one-liners during his many
OL,16,Fpress conferences and media interviews.
OL,18,FHere are just a few of our favourites:
