OL,3,CTop of the Klopps: Jurgen's best quotes
OL,5,FHe wasted no time at his very first
OL,6,FLiverpool press conference, charming
OL,7,Fhis way through the many questions.
OL,9,F"I don't want to describe myself. I'm
OL,10,Fa totally normal guy. I came from the
OL,11,FBlack Forest. I'm the 'Normal One'."
OL,13,FBefore adding: "All the people told me
OL,14,Fso much about the British press and so
OL,15,Fit is up to you to show me they are
OL,16,Fall liars."
OL,18,FThen there was the time he laughed off
OL,19,Ffears Liverpool would be humiliated by
OL,20,Fhis former club.
