OL,3,CTop of the Klopps: Jurgen's best quotes
OL,5,FHe played down the significance of his
OL,6,Freturn to Borussia Dortmund for the
OL,7,FEuropa League quarter-final.
OL,9,FHe told reporters: "I had a wonderful
OL,10,Ftime. It is better to be here than in,
OL,11,FI don't know, North Korea."
OL,13,FHe was also never afraid to give as
OL,14,Fgood as he got from inquisitive
OL,15,Fjournalists:
OL,17,F"Are you well? Because you (the
OL,18,Freporter) don't look well!"
