OL,3,CTop of the Klopps: Jurgen's best quotes
OL,5,FOften self-deprecating, he once
OL,6,Ffamously compared his appearance to
OL,7,Fthat of a serial killer.
OL,9,FHe was asked about new black-rimmed
OL,10,Fglasses which had given him a changed
OL,11,Fappearance. Klopp responded: "Not new,
OL,12,Fonly the second pair. They are black.
OL,14,F"I look a little bit like a serial
OL,15,Fkiller, but you (the reporter) look
OL,16,Flike one too."
OL,18,FOn another occasion, he laughed off
OL,19,Fthe moment he broke his glasses while
OL,20,Fcelebrating his side's win with player
OL,21,FAdam Lallana.
