OL,3,CTop of the Klopps: Jurgen's best quotes
OL,5,F"I don't know, I saw nothing. Usually
OL,6,FI have a second pair, but I couldn't
OL,7,Ffind them.
OL,9,F"It's really difficult looking for
OL,10,Fglasses without glasses."
OL,12,FOf course, sometimes his passion did
OL,13,Fboil over into frustration.
OL,15,FIn November 2023, he was furious when
OL,16,FToulouse fans drowned out his press
OL,17,Fconference with boisterous
OL,18,Fcelebrations after he was made to hold
OL,19,Fit in a tent.
