OL,5,FNo supporters were inside but
OL,6,Freporters could not hear Klopp over
OL,7,Fthe banging from outside.
OL,9,F"Who had the idea to do a press
OL,10,Fconference here - that would be a
OL,11,Freally interesting question. Wow!" he
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,FAnd then there was the time when
OL,15,FLiverpool fan Daniel Craig tipped
OL,16,FKlopp to be the next 007.
OL,18,F"I don't want to be James Bond.
