OL,3,CTop of the Klopps: Jurgen's best quotes
OL,5,F"Thank you for having these nice words
OL,6,Fbut I would be a really bad James Bond
OL,7,Fbecause if I walk out of the water in
OL,8,Fswim shorts, I think that would be the
OL,9,Fmoment that all the whole world would
OL,10,Fswitch off.
OL,12,F"No problem, we all have our own jobs
OL,13,Fto do in life, and he has to save the
OL,14,Fworld and I have to help Liverpool."
OL,16,FAnd he was certainly the hero
OL,17,FLiverpool needed, ending their 30-year
OL,18,Ftitle drought and claiming their sixth
OL,19,FEuropean Cup.
